4/09/FoutTet-Ellie-Goulding-collaborarive-single-In-My-Dreams.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/FoutTet-Ellie-Goulding-collaborarive-single-In-My-Dreams-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/FoutTet-Ellie-Goulding-collaborarive-single-In-My-Dreams-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/FoutTet-Ellie-Goulding-collaborarive-single-In-My-Dreams-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/FoutTet-Ellie-Goulding-collaborarive-single-In-My-Dreams-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/FoutTet-Ellie-Goulding-collaborarive-single-In-My-Dreams-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/four-tet">Four Tet</a>再次与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ellie-goulding">Ellie Goulding</a>联手推出合作新单曲“In My Dreams”——请听下面。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/ellie-goulding-higher-than-heaven-review-3426776">埃莉·古尔丁 (Ellie Goulding) – 《高于天堂》评论：个人驱动流行音乐的俏皮解药</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-four-tets-bubbling-ellie-goulding-collab-baby-2600565">两人此前曾合作制作了 Four Tet 2020 年的歌曲《Baby》</a> ，该歌曲出现在这位电子艺术家的第十张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/four-tet-announces-new-album-sixteen-oceans-2599651">《Sixteen Oceans》</a>中。 2022 年，后者重新混音了古尔丁的歌曲《Easy Lover》，为他赢得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-nominations-2023-beyonce-kendrick-lamar-adele-and-harry-styles-score-the-most-nods-3349585">格莱美最佳混音唱片类别的提名</a>。</p><p>谈到他如何在《In My Dreams》中与这位流行歌手重聚，Four Tet（真名 Kieren Hebden）解释道：“她过去告诉我，她喜欢向我发送人声，我可以将其用作声音，然后将其变成任何东西。”我想要（这就是几年前歌曲“Baby”的发生方式）。</p><p> “我找到了与之相配的其他声音并制作了《In My Dreams》。她添加了一些新的声音部分，但我们最终保留了语音笔记录音作为主要声音。我想第一次拍摄往往是最神奇的。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="在我的梦里" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/N-DpHeO_vA4?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>古尔丁在社交媒体上谈到此次新合作时说道：“你们大多数人都知道我是在电子音乐和舞曲音乐的陪伴下长大的，在我 20 岁出头的时候发现《Four Tet》就像潜入了一个宝箱。</p><p> “当我不久前联系他时，他从来没有质疑过，也没有任何愤世嫉俗的态度，只是让我有时给他发一些声音。像基兰这样伟大的制作人像乐器一样简单地采样我的声音是我一直渴望的，即使是以最简单的方式，我也觉得我从作为歌手的工作中获得了最大的乐趣。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_tN_w4ORYe/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,