查佩尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan) 表示，她之前的唱片公司不希望她发行《Pink Pony Club》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-says-her-previous-label-didnt-want-her-to-release-pink-pony-club-3792531?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=查佩尔·罗恩说她以前的标签不想让她发行粉红小马俱乐部Surej SinghWed, 11 Sep 2024 06:04:16 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3792531 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Chappell Roan 将于 2024 年 2 月 23 日在加利福尼亚州棕榈泉 Acrisure Arena 为 GUTS 世界巡演拉开序幕表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “证明他们错了感觉真好，因为他们错得不只是一点点”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-says-her-previous-label-didnt-want-her-to-release-pink-pony-club-3792531">Chappell Roan 表示她之前的唱片公司不希望她发行《Pink Pony Club》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Chappell Roan 将于 2024 年 2 月 23 日在加利福尼亚州棕榈泉 Acrisure Arena 为 GUTS 世界巡演拉开序幕表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>艺术家透露，查普尔·罗恩 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">Chappell Roan</a> ) 最受欢迎的歌曲之一《Pink Pony Club》几乎被她之前的唱片公司阻止发行。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-chapell-roan-interview-the-rise-and-fall-of-a-midwest-princess-3582467">Chappell Roan：流行超新星，感觉就像“变装皇后”女孩之一</a></strong></li></ul><p>2020 年，查佩尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan) 通过大西洋唱片公司发行了单曲“Pink Pony Club”。几个月后，她被该厂牌抛弃了。去年，她通过 Island and Amusement Records 发行了首张专辑《The Rise And Fall Of A Midwest Princess》，其中收录有《Pink Pony Club》，并成为她最受欢迎的热门歌曲之一。</p><p>然而，情况并非总是如此，这位创作型歌手在<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/chappell-roan-good-luck-babe-fame-fans-1235094314/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《滚石》</em></a>的一篇新专题中透露，大西洋唱片公司坚决反对她发行这首歌。她回忆说，唱片公司曾试图阻止她发行这首歌，因为这与她以前的声音有很大不同。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Chappell Roan - Pink Pony Club（官方音乐视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/GR3Liudev18?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “我非常沮丧，”她告诉该出版物。 “这让我重新审视自己。”这首歌最初的反应是积极的，但直到 2023 年她的首张专辑发行后才真正爆发。她和联合制作人尼格罗回忆起为将这首歌通过大西洋推广而奋斗的经历，因为他们坚信这首歌会吸引更多的听众。</p><p>现在这首歌风靡全球，罗恩重新相信自己的直觉：“证明他们错了感觉真好，因为他们错得不只是一点点。他们真的、真的、真的错了。知道我的直觉是正确的，这是世界上最好的感觉。有目的的报复感觉不太好，但是无意中的报复感觉很棒。”</p><p>在聊天的其他地方，她透露<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-shares-update-on-weird-new-album-3792501">她的第二张专辑进展顺利</a>，她已经完成了五六首歌曲：“我们有一首乡村歌曲。我们有一首舞曲。我们有一种真正的八十年代风格，我们有一种原声音乐，还有一种真正有机的、现场乐队的、七十年代的氛围。这真是太奇怪了。” </p><figure id="attachment_3582574" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3582574" style="width: 2160px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3582574" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/NME-THE-COVER-2024-CHAPPELL-ROAN-COVER-CREDIT-KRISTEN-JAN-WONG-3@2160X2700.jpg" alt="NME 2024 年封面 CHAPPELL ROAN 摄影：KRISTEN JAN WONG" width="2160" height="2700" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/NME-THE-COVER-2024-CHAPPELL-ROAN-COVER-CREDIT-KRISTEN-JAN-WONG-3@2160X2700.jpg 2160w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/NME-THE-COVER-2024-CHAPPELL-ROAN-COVER-CREDIT-KRISTEN-JAN-WONG-3@2160X2700-400x500.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/NME-THE-COVER-2024-CHAPPELL-ROAN-COVER-CREDIT-KRISTEN-JAN-WONG-3@2160X2700-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/NME-THE-COVER-2024-CHAPPELL-ROAN-COVER-CREDIT-KRISTEN-JAN-WONG-3@2160X2700-696x870.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/NME-THE-COVER-2024-CHAPPELL-ROAN-COVER-CREDIT-KRISTEN-JAN-WONG-3@2160X2700-1392x1740.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/NME-THE-COVER-2024-CHAPPELL-ROAN-COVER-CREDIT-KRISTEN-JAN-WONG-3@2160X2700-1068x1335.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2160px) 100vw, 2160px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3582574" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：NME 的 Kristen Jan Wong</figcaption></figure><p>这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-chapell-roan-interview-the-rise-and-fall-of-a-midwest-princess-3582467"><em>《NME》</em>封面明星</a>去年九月发行了她的首张录音室专辑“The Rise And Fall Of A Midwest Princess”，广受好评。 <i>《NME》</i>在一篇<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/lollapalooza">四星评论</a>中将其描述为“罗恩大胆而厚颜无耻的笔的展示，她在其中将灼热的启示与一些可爱的厚颜无耻的合唱一起放置”。</p><p>从那时起，她的第一张专辑在发行近一年后就获得了英国冠军—— <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elton-john-congratulates-chappell-roan-on-chart-success-the-meteoric-rise-of-a-midwestern-princess-3782611">埃尔顿·约翰最近对此表示祝贺</a>。罗恩分享了单曲“祝你好运，宝贝！”今年四月。这首歌在英国排名第四，并于六月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/check-out-sabrina-carpenters-stripped-back-cover-of-chappell-roans-good-luck-babe-for-bbc-radio-one-live-lounge-3766709">在 BBC Live Lounge 被 Sabrina Carpenter 翻唱</a>。</p><p>查佩尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan) 名声大噪， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roans-lollapalooza-set-is-among-the-festivals-most-attended-in-history-3781184">上个月吸引了 Lollapalooza 历史上最大规模的日间观众</a>，Lolla 代表证实了这一点。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-says-her-previous-label-didnt-want-her-to-release-pink-pony-club-3792531">Chappell Roan 表示她之前的唱片公司不希望她发行《Pink Pony Club》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
